### Development Setup

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/trendsagi/TrendsAGI.git
cd TrendsAGI

# Install development dependencies
pip install -e ".[dev]"

# Run tests
pytest

# Run linting
flake8 trendsagi/
mypy trendsagi/
```

